  "text": "We design a distributed state estimator -similar to the one given in [CITATION_1] -based on a full-order Luenberger-like observer and used by each DGU to estimate its local state. This requires local model information, as well as output measurements that are communicated from its neighbors and are subject to possible attacks.",
